This project is a fully static Vite + React site deployed on Vercel.

Rules:

Never reintroduce SSR, TanStack Start, Nitro, or any server-side rendering
Always keep build output as dist/
The entry point must remain index.html in the project root
Must always use vite build (not bun, not custom server builds)
Vercel deployment must remain static (no server functions)
Do not add or modify server/ folder or server entry files
All routing must be client-side only (React Router / TanStack Router if used)
Any changes must preserve successful npm run build

If unsure, prefer the simplest static Vite solution.